  "ask.hero_subtitle": "NuriaOne is a faith-first AI assistant for the questions that matter most. Grounded in authentic sources, governed by qualified scholars, and built never to hallucinate. The reassurance that ChatGPT, Gemini and other models simply cannot give you.",
