  "ask.step1_text": "Pose your question in your own words and language. As openly or as privately as you wish.",
  "ask.step1_title": "You ask",
  "ask.step2_text": "NuriaOne searches a curated library of the Qur'an, authentic Hadith and trusted scholarship. Not the open internet.",
  "ask.step2_title": "We retrieve the sources",
  "ask.step3_text": "Our guardrails and scholar governance check every claim against its evidence and remove anything uncertain.",
  "ask.step3_title": "The halal layer verifies",
  "ask.step4_text": "A clear, compassionate reply. With its sources shown, so you can verify it for yourself.",
  "ask.step4_title": "You receive the answer",
  "ask.trust1": "Built never to hallucinate",
  "ask.trust2": "Grounded in Qur'an & authentic Hadith",
  "ask.trust3": "Every answer shows its sources",
  "ask.trust4": "Governed by qualified scholars",
  "ask.use1_text": "Clear, sourced answers on worship, transactions and daily life. With the evidence and the differences of opinion made plain.",
  "ask.use1_title": "Fiqh & rulings",
  "ask.use2_text": "Explore verses with faithful translation and classical commentary. Never a fabricated ayah, never a verse out of context.",
  "ask.use2_title": "Qur'an & Tafsir",
  "ask.use3_text": "Ask about a narration and NuriaOne checks its grading and chain. So you are never handed a weak or invented hadith as if it were sound.",
  "ask.use3_title": "Hadith, authenticated",
  "ask.use4_text": "Prayer, fasting, zakat, hajj and purification. Practical, step-by-step guidance rooted in authentic teaching.",
  "ask.use4_title": "Worship & practice",
  "ask.use5_text": "Bring the weight on your heart. Grief, doubt, temptation, repentance. And receive compassionate counsel anchored in the deen.",
  "ask.use5_title": "Personal struggles",
  "ask.use6_text": "Ask in Arabic, Urdu, Indonesian, French, Turkish, English and more. And receive the same trustworthy answer, natively.",
  "ask.use6_title": "In your language",
  "ask.uses_label": "Use cases",
  "ask.uses_subtitle": "From everyday worship to the heaviest matters of the heart. NuriaOne meets you with knowledge you can trust, in your own language.",
  "ask.uses_title": "Answers for the questions <em>that matter most</em>",
  "ask.why_c1_text": "General models will confidently fabricate rulings, misquote the Qur'an, and attribute hadith that were never spoken. NuriaOne refuses to guess. If it is not certain, it tells you.",
  "ask.why_c1_title": "They invent with confidence",
  "ask.why_c2_text": "Mainstream AI mixes schools, sects and opinions into one vague answer. NuriaOne respects your madhhab, keeps positions distinct, and is clear about where scholars differ.",
  "ask.why_c2_title": "They blur the lines",
  "ask.why_c3_text": "No scholar oversees ChatGPT or Gemini. NuriaOne is developed in collaboration with qualified muftis and anchored to authentic sources. Accountable to the tradition, by design.",
  "ask.why_c3_title": "They answer to no one",
  "ask.why_label": "Why NuriaOne",
  "ask.why_subtitle": "General-purpose AI was built to sound confident. Not to protect your deen. For sensitive religious questions, that is a risk no believer should have to take. NuriaOne is built differently.",
  "ask.why_title": "For your faith, <em>&ldquo;probably right&rdquo;</em> is not good enough",
