  "company.belief_ai_text": "When a machine speaks about the deen, it must be more careful than any of us would be. Not less. NuriaOne cites its sources, admits what it does not know, and never invents a fatwa.",
  "company.belief_ai_title": "AI is held to a higher standard than we hold ourselves.",
  "company.belief_label": "What we believe",
  "company.belief_locked_text": "Not by wealth, language, or tradition. Nuria serves every Muslim. Equally. No tradition-based gating, no quiet decision about who counts.",
  "company.belief_locked_title": "No Muslim locked out.",
  "company.belief_madhab_text": "Hanafi, Maliki, Shafi'i, Hanbali. Treated as living traditions, not a dropdown filter you tolerate. Your fiqh is how you pray. So Nuria meets you there.",
  "company.belief_madhab_title": "Your madhab. Your way.",
  "company.belief_precision_text": "Prayer times are one of the five pillars. Nuria calculates yours by your exact location, every day. When you stand before Allah, you should not be guessing whether you are on time.",
  "company.belief_precision_title": "Precision is an act of worship.",
  "company.belief_product_text": "The Quran is free. Prayer times are free. The Qibla, the dhikr, the duas. Free. Always. We will never put a paywall between a Muslim and their prayer.",
  "company.belief_product_title": "Your deen is not a product.",
  "company.belief_title": "Constraints we chose. And you can hold us to.",
  "company.close_body": "There was a night when one new Muslim sat alone with a phone full of half-answers. Out of that night came a light meant for 1.8 billion more.",
  "company.close_cta": "Come home to Nuria.",
  "company.close_kalima": "There is no god but Allah. And no Muslim should ever have to find Him alone.",
  "company.close_light": "A light that doesn't dim when it's shared.",
  "company.close_verse": "\"Verily, with hardship comes ease.\"",
  "company.close_verse_ref": "Surah Al-Inshirah, 94:5",
  "company.commit_1": "The core deen is free. No paywall between a Muslim and their prayer. We never charge for the Quran.",
  "company.commit_2": "No Muslim locked out. Every Muslim served equally. No tradition-based gating.",
  "company.commit_3": "Every madhab honoured as a living tradition. Hanafi, Maliki, Shafi'i, Hanbali.",
  "company.commit_4": "NuriaOne cites its sources. Or it stays silent. No invented fatwas. No false confidence.",
  "company.commit_5": "You never pay to practice. Serene and Noor are one-time; Advanced NuriaOne is always a choice. Never a gate on the deen.",
  "company.commit_6": "We will never inflate what we are. The trust of one Muslim is an amanah.",
  "company.commit_label": "Our commitment",
  "company.commit_title": "These are not features. They are constraints we chose.",
  "company.contact_line": "Press, partners, and investors: hello@nuria.one",
  "company.cta_btn": "Download Nuria",
  "company.cta_text": "Download Nuria, follow our story, and grow with a global community of believers.",
  "company.cta_title": "Join us on the journey",
  "company.free_core": "The deen is free. The Quran with audio, prayer times, the Qibla, your daily dhikr and duas, the first path to reading Arabic. Free, for every Muslim, forever. You will never pay to practice your faith. That line does not move.",
  "company.free_intro": "A free deen still has to be paid for. We are honest about how. Because the way a company makes its money tells you exactly who it really serves. So here is the whole model, with nothing hidden.",
  "company.free_label": "How we keep the deen free",
  "company.free_principle": "You never pay to practice. You pay only to go deeper, to personalise, or to sustain. And every time you do, you keep the deen free for a Muslim who can't.",
  "company.free_tier_advanced_text": "Our most advanced source-cited Islamic AI. The one thing that recurs. Because trustworthy AI costs real money to run every day.",
  "company.free_tier_advanced_title": "Advanced NuriaOne. Subscription (coming)",
  "company.free_tier_free_text": "Quran, prayer times, Qibla, dhikr, duas, Qaida, Halqa, and core NuriaOne. Supported by discreet, Islamic-compliant ads, never between you and your salah.",
  "company.free_tier_free_title": "Nuria. Free, always",
  "company.free_tier_iap_text": "Optional cosmetic extras. Tasbih designs, theme touches. Delight, never access.",
  "company.free_tier_iap_title": "À la carte",
  "company.free_tier_noor_text": "Premium ad-free, plus the Luxury Stone theme and other premium touches. Still one-time. Beauty, never access.",
  "company.free_tier_noor_title": "Nuria Noor. One-time",
  "company.free_tier_serene_text": "A single purchase that lifts the ads and supports the mission. Not a subscription.",
  "company.free_tier_serene_title": "Nuria Serene. One-time",
  "company.free_title": "You never pay to practice.",
  "company.hero_label": "Nuria Technologies",
  "company.hero_subtitle": "Nuria Technologies builds beautiful, trustworthy digital tools for the Muslim world. With Nuria, our Islamic companion, at the heart of everything we do.",
  "company.hero_title": "Light for a <em>billion</em> hearts",
  "company.lead_sub": "Nuria Technologies is building the digital home the global ummah has never had. And the Islamic AI infrastructure the world needs before it can trust what it hears about the deen.",
  "company.lead_title": "Built for the Muslim. <em>Not built off the Muslim.</em>",
  "company.meta_desc": "Two brothers. One night. A company built for 1.8 billion Muslims. The digital home for the global ummah. Free for every Muslim. Always.",
  "company.meta_title": "Our Story. Nuria Technologies",
  "company.metric1_label": "Languages",
  "company.metric1_num": "100+",
  "company.metric2_label": "Ummah, United",
  "company.metric2_num": "1",
  "company.metric3_label": "Hearts We Aim to Reach",
  "company.metric3_num": "Millions",
  "company.mirror_born": "To the one born into it. The words are muscle memory, but somewhere between the school run and the inbox the dhikr got quiet. You are not lapsed. You are tired. Nuria puts it back within arm's reach. Your madhab, your way.",
  "company.mirror_close": "Born, reverted, returning. The ummah is one body. We are building for the whole body.",
  "company.mirror_label": "The mirror",
  "company.mirror_returning": "To the one finding the way back. You never stopped believing, you just stopped showing up. There is no lecture here and no ledger of your absence. Only the next prayer, the next ayah, the next breath of dhikr.",
  "company.mirror_revert": "To the one who just arrived. You said the words, the sky did not change but everything did, and then the silence: now what? You are not behind. You are at the beginning of the best thing that will ever happen to you. We built your first day.",
  "company.mirror_title": "Three Muslims. One ache. This is for all of you.",
  "company.num1_label": "Muslims onboard",
  "company.num1_num": "50,000+",
  "company.num2_label": "Countries",
  "company.num2_num": "11",
  "company.num3_label": "Languages",
  "company.num3_num": "100+",
  "company.num4_label": "The ummah we serve",
  "company.num4_num": "1.8B",
  "company.num_label": "By the numbers",
  "company.num_title": "Not projections. Muslims praying with Nuria right now.",
  "company.page_title": "About Nuria Technologies. Light for a Billion Hearts",
  "company.sphere_app_text": "The full Quran word-by-word with audio, precise prayer times, the Qibla, dhikr, duas, and Qaida learning paths. Free, always.",
  "company.sphere_app_title": "Nuria. The companion in your pocket",
  "company.sphere_family_text": "Connect your family inside the app, and add a cloud legacy and bequest layer. A light handed down, not an account that ends when you do.",
  "company.sphere_family_title": "Family Deen Tree. Passing the light forward",
  "company.sphere_halqa_text": "Accountability circles, made of love. Build a circle with family, friends, your study group; set goals together; show up for one another. The ummah is one body.",
  "company.sphere_halqa_title": "Halqa. You were never meant to do this alone",
  "company.sphere_intel_text": "An Islamic knowledge layer in scholarly review, exposed through open interfaces so other apps and tools can build on source-grounded Islamic knowledge instead of hallucinated fatwas. The moat is not the model. The moat is the trust.",
  "company.sphere_intel_title": "Nuria Intelligence. The foundation beneath",
  "company.sphere_intro": "Walk through it room by room. Nothing was bolted on. Each piece assumes the others.",
  "company.sphere_label": "The Sphere",
  "company.sphere_nuriaone_text": "Our source-citing Islamic AI: it answers from authentic sources and cites them, says what it does not know, and never issues a binding fatwa. Ask NuriaOne anything. And know where the answer comes from.",
  "company.sphere_nuriaone_title": "NuriaOne. A scholarly companion, not a chatbot",
  "company.sphere_remove": "Remove any single room and the home has a draft running through it.",
  "company.sphere_title": "One home for the whole life of a Muslim.",
  "company.team_label": "The People Behind Nuria",
  "company.team_title": "A small team with one intention",
  "company.v1_text": "Every feature is shaped by Islam and refined together with Muslims. We honour the deen in both what we build and how we build it.",
  "company.v1_title": "Built on Faith",
  "company.v2_text": "Privacy-first, secure, and crafted to the highest standard. We build calm, ad-light experiences that respect your time and your trust.",
  "company.v2_title": "Engineered to Last",
  "company.v3_text": "In 100+ languages, on every device. Nuria is made to serve Muslims everywhere. No one left behind.",
  "company.v3_title": "For the Whole Ummah",
  "company.vision_label": "Our Vision",
  "company.vision_p1": "We believe technology should bring people closer to their faith, never distract them from it. Our vision is simple and vast: that millions of Muslims, in every country and language, open Nuria each day to pray, reflect, and grow.",
  "company.vision_p2": "Nuria Technologies is the company being built around that mission. A focused studio creating sincere, secure, and genuinely beautiful software for the ummah, for the long term.",
  "company.vision_title": "An app in every Muslim&rsquo;s hand",
  "company.who_label": "Who we are",
  "company.who_p1": "Not one tool among many. The home where the deen lives whole: the Quran with audio, prayer times, the Qibla, dhikr, learning, community, and trustworthy answers, gathered under one light.",
  "company.who_p2": "We are not a startup that went looking for a market. We are two brothers who went looking for an answer. And built it when they could not find it anywhere else. We changed the name to Nuria Technologies not to sound bigger, but to be honest about the scope: a single app fixes one screen; a company can build a whole sphere. And treat the deen as a trust, not a market.",
  "company.who_title": "The place a Muslim opens first.",
  "company.whynow_text": "The next generation is coming online. The youngest, fastest-growing Muslim populations, getting their first smartphones now. AI is about to answer religious questions whether we are ready or not. The only question is whether those answers are grounded and cited, or confident and wrong. And the ummah is tired of being the product. The window is open. We intend to be the ones standing in it.",
  "company.whynow_title": "Why now",
  "cookie.accept": "Accept cookies",
  "cookie.aria_label": "Cookie consent",
  "cookie.decline": "Decline",
  "cookie.message_html": "We only store an essential cookie to remember your preference. Optional analytics are used only if you accept. Read our <a href=\"/cookies\">Cookie Policy</a>, <a href=\"/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a>, and <a href=\"/terms\">Terms of Service</a>.",
  "cookie.title": "Your cookie choice",
  "cookies_page.meta": "<strong>Effective date:</strong> 9 June 2026 &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; <strong>Last updated:</strong> 9 June 2026",
  "cookies_page.s1_text": "This Cookie Policy explains how Nuria (\"we\", \"us\", \"our\") uses cookies and similar local storage on the Nuria website. The Nuria app may show advertising (see our Privacy Policy §2.19); this page covers website cookies only.",
  "cookies_page.s1_title": "1. Overview",
  "cookies_page.s2_li1": "<strong>Consent preference:</strong> The key <code>nuria_cookie_consent_v1</code> stores whether you accepted or declined optional analytics. This is required to remember your choice and to avoid repeatedly showing the consent banner.",
  "cookies_page.s2_li2": "<strong>Website theme preference:</strong> The key <code>nuria-site-theme</code> stores whether you chose Classic or Luxury Stone. This stays in your browser and lets every page keep the same theme after navigation or reloads.",
  "cookies_page.s2_li3": "<strong>Referral and portal helpers:</strong> Certain partner or referral flows may temporarily use browser state, URL parameters, or Firebase session storage to complete a join, login, claim-link, or portal action. These values support navigation and access control rather than advertising.",
  "cookies_page.s2_text": "We use a small number of cookie-equivalent values in browser local storage:",
  "cookies_page.s2_title": "2. Cookies We Use",
  "cookies_page.s3_text": "Optional analytics are activated only if you explicitly choose \"Accept cookies\" in the consent banner. When accepted, the site loads Google Analytics 4 in a privacy-conscious configuration to measure aggregate page usage, such as whether visitors can reach support, legal, download, and 4.3 release information. If you choose \"Decline\", optional analytics remain disabled and your decline preference is remembered.",
  "cookies_page.s3_title": "3. Optional Analytics",
  "cookies_page.s4_text": "This website always loads Google Fonts. If you accept optional analytics, the site also loads Google Analytics 4 from Google. Your browser may therefore connect to Google's servers, which can include processing of your IP address and basic device/browser metadata by Google.",
  "cookies_page.s4_title": "4. Third-Party Resources",
  "cookies_page.s5_text": "You can clear local storage in your browser settings to reset your cookie preference. After clearing, the consent banner will be shown again and you can choose a new preference.",
  "cookies_page.s5_title": "5. How to Change Your Preference",
  "cookies_page.s6_text": "For any questions about this Cookie Policy, contact us at <a href=\"mailto:hello@nuria.one\">hello@nuria.one</a>.",
  "cookies_page.s6_title": "6. Contact",
  "daily.d1_text": "A carefully chosen verse from the Holy Quran or the Hadith of the Prophet ㋞, accompanied by reflection and context to deepen your connection with the Divine Word.",
  "daily.d1_title": "Daily Scripture",
  "daily.d2_text": "Meet a luminary of the Islamic tradition. A Companion, a great Imam, a scholar of the heart. Each day, a new light from our tradition to inspire your own journey.",
  "daily.d2_title": "Daily Role Model",
  "daily.d3_text": "Your daily spiritual companion. A reflection crafted with wisdom and intention, speaking directly to where you are on your path. Every single day.",
  "daily.d3_title": "Personal Reflection",
  "daily.label": "What Awaits You Each Day",
  "daily.showcase_caption": "Another glimpse of Nuria in everyday life.",
  "daily.showcase_label": "Your day, gently held",
  "daily.showcase_lead": "Morning scripture, role models, and reflection. Nuria meets you where you are.",
  "daily.title": "Every Morning, a New <em>Blessing</em>",
  "del.app_text": "The fastest way to delete your account is directly inside Nuria: go to <strong>Settings → Account → Delete Account</strong> and follow the steps.",
  "del.app_title": "Delete in the App",
  "del.btn_cancel": "Cancel & Go Back",
  "del.btn_submit": "Request Account Deletion",
  "del.email_text": "You can also email us at <a href=\"mailto:hello@nuria.one\">hello@nuria.one</a> with the subject \"Account Deletion Request\" and we will process it within 30 days.",
  "del.email_title": "Request via Email",
  "del.form_desc": "Use the form below to submit a formal account deletion request. Please provide the email address linked to your Nuria account.",
  "del.form_title": "Submit a Deletion Request",
  "del.help_text": "Before you go, we would love to help if something isn't working. Please reach out at <a href=\"mailto:hello@nuria.one\">hello@nuria.one</a> or visit our <a href=\"/support\">Support Center</a>. We're here for you, in shaa Allah.",
  "del.help_title": "Need Help Instead?",
  "del.label_email": "Email Address on your Nuria account",
  "del.label_notes": "Additional notes (optional)",
  "del.label_reason": "Reason for leaving (optional)",
  "del.next_intro": "After we receive your request:",
  "del.next_li1": "We will send a confirmation email to the address you provided.",
  "del.next_li2": "Your account will be scheduled for deletion within <strong>30 days</strong>.",
  "del.next_li3": "During this period, you can cancel the deletion request by contacting <a href=\"mailto:hello@nuria.one\">hello@nuria.one</a>.",
  "del.next_li4": "After 30 days, all personal data associated with your account will be permanently and irreversibly deleted from our systems.",
  "del.next_li5": "Some anonymised, non-identifiable usage data may be retained for statistical purposes only.",
  "del.next_li6": "Version 4.3 feature records, including learning progress, theme preferences, personalized settings, achievements, partner/referral links tied to your account, and support correspondence connected to the deletion request, are reviewed under the same privacy and retention rules.",
  "del.next_title": "What Happens Next",
  "del.ph_notes": "Any additional information or feedback you would like to share with us…",
  "del.r0": "I'd rather not say",
  "del.r1": "I no longer use the app",
