  "del.warn_li2": "Your reflection history will be deleted and cannot be recovered.",
  "del.warn_li3": "If you have active recurring billing for Nuria through Apple or Google (legacy accounts only), cancel it in the store <strong>before</strong> deleting your account. Serene and Noor one-time purchases do not need cancellation.",
  "del.warn_li4": "Unused reflections and Serene or Noor benefits do not transfer to a new account.",
