  "release.band_410": "Hiba gifts, Qaida, Sunnat, Nuria Points, Luxury Stone polish, notifications, and release hardening that set the foundation for today's companion.",
  "release.band_430": "Free with ads, Serene & Noor IAP, rewarded reflection bonuses, Nuria Journey cloud sync, Quran word-by-word audio fixes, grandfathered ad-free legacy accounts, and localization polish across 100+ languages.",
  "release.band_site": "Preview the Luxury Stone palette on this website. The same premium theme Nuria Noor unlocks in the app.",
  "release.card1_text": "Nuria Noor unlocks a warm stone surface system with dark emerald CTAs, gilded rules, procedural veining, texture-aware widgets, and a live preview in settings.",
  "release.card1_title": "Luxury Stone with Nuria Noor",
  "release.card2_text": "Full-mushaf playback, mini-player controls, corrected word-by-word audio mapping, verse-jump landing, bookmarks, Juz tracking, ayah notes, tajweed sheets, reciter picker, source-locked tafsir, and Quranic Corpus word study.",
  "release.card2_title": "Word-by-word audio and study depth",
  "release.card3_text": "Nuria Journey now mirrors weekly history to the cloud, sorts journey days reliably, auto-unlocks rewards, and keeps Halqa, Qaida, and scholar-path progress feeling connected across sessions.",
  "release.card3_title": "Weekly Nuria Journey in the cloud",
  "release.card4_text": "The full app stays free with thoughtful banner, native, and interstitial ads. Nuria Serene removes ads forever; Nuria Noor adds Luxury Stone and 300 bonus reflections. Optional rewarded ads still earn bonus reflections on the free tier.",
  "release.card4_title": "Free with ads, Serene & Noor",
  "release.label": "Version 4.0.0 to 4.3",
  "release.subtitle": "4.3 completes Nuria's shift to a free ad-supported app with Nuria Serene and Nuria Noor one-time purchases, Nuria Journey cloud sync, sharper Quran word-by-word audio, rewarded reflection bonuses, and polish across 100+ languages. Building on Luxury Stone, Halqa, Qaida, Sunnat, and Live Haramain.",
  "release.title": "Free with ads, Serene & Noor, and a fuller companion",
  "site.index_desc": "Free Quran, prayer tools, Ask Nuria, and daily Islamic guidance. Remove ads with Nuria Serene, or unlock Luxury Stone and 300 bonus reflections with Nuria Noor.",
  "site.index_og_desc": "Download Nuria free with ads, or choose Nuria Serene (ad-free) or Nuria Noor (Luxury Stone + bonus reflections).",
  "site.index_og_title": "Nuria. Free Islamic Companion | Serene & Noor",
  "site.index_title": "Nuria. Free Islamic Companion | Serene & Noor",
  "sources.card_ai_point_1": "Prompt source scope: Quran, authenticated hadith, the Companions, and recognised Sunni scholars.",
  "sources.card_ai_point_2": "Blocked before generation: medical advice, mental health and self-harm, extremism, and fatwa or halal-haram ruling requests.",
  "sources.card_ai_point_3": "Operational controls: App Check is enforced and requests are rate limited before a reply is returned.",
  "sources.card_ai_text": "Ask Nuria is designed to respond with guidance rooted in the Quran, Hadith, and mainstream Sunni teaching. It is meant to support reflection and comfort, not to invent rulings or replace qualified scholars.",
  "sources.card_ai_title": "Ask Nuria and AI guidance",
  "sources.card_audio_point_1": "Per-ayah recitation delivery: everyayah.com.",
  "sources.card_audio_point_2": "Reciters: curated catalogue including Alafasy, Al-Sudais, Al-Shuraim, Al-Muaiqly, Al-Minshawi, Al-Husary, Abdul Basit, and Hani Ar-Rifai.",
  "sources.card_audio_text": "Quran recitations and selected audio are sourced from licensed, public, or otherwise rights-respecting providers, including sources such as EveryAyah where appropriate.",
  "sources.card_audio_title": "Recitations, audio, and talks",
  "sources.card_devotional_point_1": "Each item keeps its own source reference inside Nuria's devotional data or content storage.",
  "sources.card_devotional_point_2": "Cited source families include Quran, Sahih al-Bukhari, Sahih Muslim, Jami al-Tirmidhi, Sunan Abi Dawud, and Ibn Majah.",
  "sources.card_devotional_text": "Nuria's devotional collections are curated in app data and content storage with a source attached to each item. The cited references include Quran verses and hadith collections such as Sahih al-Bukhari, Sahih Muslim, Jami al-Tirmidhi, Sunan Abi Dawud, and Ibn Majah.",
  "sources.card_devotional_title": "Duas, adhkar, hadith, and ruqyah",
  "sources.card_dua_text": "Supplications and remembrance collections are grounded in recognised works such as Hisnul Muslim and classical hadith collections including Sahih al-Bukhari, Sahih Muslim, and Sunan Abu Dawud.",
  "sources.card_dua_title": "Duas and adhkar",
  "sources.card_editorial_text": "Daily reflections and learning content are written and reviewed with the Quran, Hadith, tafsir, Riyad as-Salihin, and other classical references as their foundation.",
  "sources.card_editorial_title": "Reflections and editorial content",
  "sources.card_prayer_point_1": "Prayer calculations: adhan library with selectable regional methods.",
  "sources.card_prayer_point_2": "Qibla: great-circle bearing from device location toward the Kaaba, using device sensors.",
  "sources.card_prayer_text": "Prayer times and Qibla direction are calculated on your device using standard astronomical and geographic formulas, your location, and compass data. For mosque schedules or critical observance, always verify locally.",
  "sources.card_prayer_title": "Prayer times and Qibla",
  "sources.card_quran_point_1": "Arabic Quran text in Nuria is served via api.alquran.cloud, which publicly credits Tanzil.net for the text and Quran Academy for edited Uthmanic text.",
  "sources.card_quran_point_2": "Translations are not taken from an open feed; Nuria uses a curated trust allowlist, mainly via api.alquran.cloud with selected editions from api.quran.com.",
  "sources.card_quran_text": "The Arabic Quran text is based on verified Quran datasets such as Tanzil, together with established translation datasets used in trusted Islamic archives. We handle presentation changes carefully and avoid casual edits to the text itself.",
  "sources.card_quran_title": "Quran text and translations",
  "sources.card_tafsir_point_1": "Tafsir generation is restricted to named works in the app's scholar catalogue.",
  "sources.card_tafsir_point_2": "Anonymous websites, blogs, social posts, unattributed API text, and AI summaries are treated as untrusted.",
  "sources.card_tafsir_text": "Tafsir explanations are tied to a named scholar catalogue inside the app. When tafsir is generated, the prompt is source locked to the selected published tafsir work and explicitly treats anonymous websites, social posts, blogs, unattributed API text, and AI summaries as untrusted.",
  "sources.card_tafsir_title": "Named tafsir works only",
  "sources.hero_label": "How Nuria is built",
  "sources.hero_stat_auth": "Verified texts",
  "sources.hero_stat_privacy": "Privacy-first design",
  "sources.hero_stat_review": "Human editorial review",
  "sources.hero_subtitle": "Every verse, dua, prayer tool, and guidance flow in Nuria should rest on a clear foundation. This page explains where the app's core content comes from and how we think about care, privacy, and accuracy.",
  "sources.hero_title": "Sources & Standards",
  "sources.intro_eyebrow": "A trustworthy foundation",
  "sources.intro_text": "Nuria combines established Islamic texts, editorial review, and on-device calculations where privacy matters. We aim to be transparent about what comes from classical sources, what reflects product guidance, and what depends on device sensors or AI.",
  "sources.intro_title": "Built on trusted Islamic references, careful product work, and privacy-conscious engineering.",
  "sources.note_text": "Prayer times, Qibla direction, and AI answers are built to support daily practice, but they do not replace your local mosque, qualified scholars, or formal religious rulings.",
  "sources.note_title": "A careful boundary",
  "sources.principle_1_text": "We try to keep sacred texts, supplications, and religious references anchored in established Sunni material rather than vague summaries or trend-driven rewrites.",
  "sources.principle_1_title": "Authenticity first",
  "sources.principle_2_text": "When a feature can be calculated on your device, we prefer that approach. This is especially important for prayer times, Qibla, and personal spiritual use.",
  "sources.principle_2_title": "Privacy by default",
  "sources.principle_3_text": "If something depends on AI, location, or device sensors, we say so clearly and encourage verification with trusted local scholars or mosques when precision matters.",
  "sources.principle_3_title": "Clarity over overclaiming",
  "sources.quote_ar": "وَقُل رَّبِّ زِدْنِي عِلْمًا",
  "sources.quote_note": "We want Nuria to stay beautiful, useful, and open to correction whenever something can be made more precise.",
  "sources.quote_ref": "Quran 20:114",
  "sources.quote_text": "\"My Lord, increase me in knowledge.\"",
  "sources.report_link": "Contact support",
  "sources.report_text": "If you notice a typo, source issue, broken reference, or anything that feels off, contact us. We review reports carefully and correct verified issues as quickly as we can.",
  "sources.report_title": "See something that looks wrong?",
  "supp.about_more": "Meet the team behind Nuria →",
  "supp.about_p1": "Nuria is built with care by a small team based in Uddevalla, Sweden. We are developers and designers with a deep interest in faith and spirituality: and Nuria was founded to honour our dear Muslim friend in the studio, whose love for Islam inspired everything you see here.",
  "supp.about_p2": "Our mission is to create thoughtful, beautiful digital tools that serve the Muslim community with sincerity and respect. Every feature, every word, and every design decision is made with your spiritual journey in mind.",
  "supp.about_quote": "\"And whoever relies upon Allah. Then He is sufficient for him.\". Quran 65:3",
  "supp.about_title": "About Nuria",
  "supp.addr_label": "Address",
  "supp.attach_note_text": "Attach up to three screenshots and describe what you expected to happen. That helps us fix issues much faster.",
  "supp.attach_note_title": "Reporting a bug?",
  "supp.card1_link": "Read the FAQ →",
  "supp.card1_text": "New to Nuria? Learn how to set up your account, explore daily features, and begin your spiritual journey with ease.",
  "supp.card1_title": "Getting Started",
  "supp.card2_link": "Learn more →",
  "supp.card2_text": "Learn how 15 starter reflections work and how personalised reflections are delivered inside Nuria.",
  "supp.card2_title": "Credits & Reflections",
  "supp.card3_link": "View answers →",
  "supp.card3_text": "Questions about Nuria Serene, Nuria Noor, billing, or refunds? We've answered the most common questions below.",
  "supp.card3_title": "Billing & Purchases",
  "supp.card4_link": "Delete account →",
  "supp.card4_text": "Need to update your account information, change settings, or request account deletion? Find everything you need here.",
  "supp.card4_title": "Account & Privacy",
  "supp.card5_link": "See what changed →",
  "supp.card5_text": "Help for the 4.3 release line: free with ads, Nuria Serene and Nuria Noor purchases, Nuria Journey sync, Luxury Stone via Noor, Quran tools, Qaida, Sunnat, Halqa, Live Haramain, and personalization.",
  "supp.card5_title": "4.3. Serene, Noor & Luxury Stone",
  "supp.contact_desc": "We read every message and aim to respond within 1–2 business days, in shaa Allah.",
  "supp.contact_label": "Support Team",
  "supp.contact_title": "Get in Touch",
  "supp.email_label": "Email",
  "supp.faq10_a": "Use the contact form below or email us at <a href=\"mailto:hello@nuria.one\">hello@nuria.one</a>. We read every message and strive to respond within 1–2 business days, in shaa Allah.",
  "supp.faq10_q": "I found an issue or have a suggestion. How do I reach you?",
  "supp.faq1_a": "Nuria is a complete Islamic companion that brings together the full Quran with audio and 40+ Quran translations in 100+ languages, daily verse, duas, adhkar, Ask Nuria, Nuria reflections across 15 categories, Qibla, prayer times, audios and speeches, companions texts, prayer guides, prayer tracking, nearest mosque finder, ruqyah, Muhasaba, Halqa, Qaida, Sunnat, Live Haramain, personalization, Luxury Stone, the Islamic calendar, and progress badges in one experience.",
  "supp.faq1_q": "What is Nuria?",
  "supp.faq2_a": "Nuria is free to download and use with advertising. Every account gets the full app. Quran, duas, prayer tools, Qaida, Ask Nuria, tracking, and more. In 100+ languages. New users receive <strong>15 starter reflections</strong>. Optional one-time purchases (Nuria Serene or Nuria Noor) remove ads permanently; Nuria Noor also unlocks Luxury Stone and includes 300 bonus reflections.",
  "supp.faq2_q": "How does Nuria work? Is it free?",
  "supp.faq3_a": "Reflections are your balance for personalised guidance in Nuria. Your balance is visible in the app. You can earn bonus reflections through optional rewarded ads, buy reflection top-ups, or choose Nuria Noor for 300 bonus reflections.",
  "supp.faq3_q": "What are credits?",
  "supp.faq4_a": "Nuria Serene and Nuria Noor are optional <strong>one-time in-app purchases</strong> that remove banner, native, and interstitial ads permanently. Nuria Noor also unlocks the Luxury Stone theme and includes 300 bonus reflections. They do not auto-renew.",
  "supp.faq4_q": "What are Nuria Serene and Nuria Noor?",
  "supp.faq5_a": "Every new device receives <strong>15 starter reflections</strong> once. You can add more through rewarded ads, reflection top-ups in Settings, or by choosing Nuria Noor.",
  "supp.faq5_q": "How many credits do I get?",
  "supp.faq6_a": "Yes. Every piece of content in Nuria is grounded in the Holy Quran, the Hadith of the Prophet ﷺ, and authentic Islamic teaching, delivered with care, warmth, and respect for the faith.",
  "supp.faq6_q": "Is the content based on authentic Islamic scholarship?",
  "supp.faq7_a": "You can keep using Nuria's daily guidance and prayer tools as normal. Watch optional rewarded ads for bonus reflections, buy a top-up in Settings, or choose Nuria Noor for a larger reflection bundle.",
  "supp.faq7_q": "What happens when I run out of credits?",
  "supp.faq8_a": "You can request account deletion from within the app (Settings → Account → Delete Account), or by visiting our <a href=\"../delete-account\">account deletion page</a>. We will permanently delete all your data within 30 days.",
  "supp.faq8_q": "How do I delete my account?",
  "supp.faq9_a": "Nuria is available on iOS via the Apple App Store and on Android via Google Play.",
  "supp.faq9_q": "On which devices can I use Nuria?",
  "supp.faq_features_a": "Nuria Qaida is a guided Quran-reading path with XP, streaks, adult and child modes. Sunnat is a searchable practice library grounded in Sahih al-Bukhari and Sahih Muslim. Live Haramain opens Makkah and Madinah live streams with prayer context. Scholar path helps tune defaults for Quran, tafsir, dhikr, prayer-time settings, and guidance tone around your preferred madhhab path.",
  "supp.faq_features_q": "What are Qaida, Sunnat, Live Haramain, and scholar path?",
  "supp.faq_release_a": "4.0.0 brought Luxury Stone (via Nuria Noor), Halqa, Qaida, Sunnat, and Live Haramain. 4.1.0 added Hiba gifts, Nuria Points, and release hardening. 4.3 makes Nuria free with ads, introduces Nuria Serene and Nuria Noor one-time purchases, Nuria Journey cloud sync, sharper Quran word-by-word audio, rewarded reflection bonuses, and polish across 100+ languages.",
  "supp.faq_release_q": "What changed from 4.0.0 to 4.3?",
  "supp.faq_stone_a": "Luxury Stone is included with <strong>Nuria Noor</strong>, a one-time purchase that also adds 300 bonus reflections and permanent ad-free access. <strong>Nuria Serene</strong> removes ads without Luxury Stone. Preview the palette on this website from the navbar theme selector.",
  "supp.faq_stone_q": "How do I get Luxury Stone?",
  "supp.faq_title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
